'''''Treasure Hunt''''' was a short story slated to appear in the canceled [[Star Wars Adventure Journal 17|''Star Wars Adventure Journal'' 17]]. In it, [[Talon Karrde]] and [[Booster Terrik]] go on a treasure hunt.

